kumara/kumera
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Polynesian sweet potato, ipomoea batatas (grown commercially by Maori farmers since the 1860s).


Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: many variant spellings in early use
